that. They
have to change and recognize the
values and

02:31.551 --> 02:33.353 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
laws of our states
unconditionally.

02:33.387 --> 02:38.392 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Parts of this
city have been
described as being as no-go
zones for women,

02:38.425 --> 02:42.195 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
but some have been out on the
streets demanding
that they should be free to move
where they

02:42.229 --> 02:47.534 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
