the events
in Cologne and elsewhere.

02:51.104 --> 02:56.043 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANGELA MERKEL, German Chancellor
(through
translator): What happened at
New Year is

02:56.076 --> 03:00.814 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
completely unacceptable. Those
are despicable
criminal acts which a state will
not accept,

03:00.847 --> 03:05.519 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
including Germany. That's why an
intensive
investigation by the relevant
institutions

03:05.552 --> 03:09.256 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
is under way. This investigation
must be supported.

03:09.289 --> 03:13.827 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The feeling women had in this
case of being
completely defenseless and at
mercy is, for

03:13.860 --> 03:18.198 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
me, personally intolerable, and
so it is important
that everything that happened
must come out

03:18.231 --> 03:22.969 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
into the open. It's right and
it's good that
there are a lot of police
reports being filed.

03:23.003 --> 03:27.541 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: These two young
Germans,
both with immigrant backgrounds,
are deeply

03:27.574 --> 03:32.379 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
