03:39.619 --> 03:44.558 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MIMOUN BERRISSOUN, Turn 180
Degrees (through
translator): When groups of
people from other

03:44.591 --> 03:48.795 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
countries come here, the first
thing they
have to do is learn the rules.
They have to

03:48.829 --> 03:52.032 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
