and can't
do.

03:52.065 --> 03:56.503 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's possible they had the idea
in their heads
that it would be easier to get
with European

03:56.536 --> 04:01.641 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
