moment.

04:10.383 --> 04:16.223 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MALCOLM BRABANT: Talha Evran,
who is of Turkish
ancestry, is worried about the
impact these

04:16.256 --> 04:19.593 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
