04:19.626 --> 04:22.829 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TALHA EVRAN, Germany: The right
wing is going
to use that as a big argument.
They have been

04:22.863 --> 04:28.168 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
